node.text:
🧁🎁😍 ‘Tis the season for baking with loved ones and with the Baileys Holiday Baking Club we’re making sure this tradition lives on! 😍😍😍 Check out episode 1 where Katherine @katherinesophie teaches @comiclonilove how to bake our famous @BaileysUS Red Velvet cupcakes. Plus, enter for a chance to win a private Zoom baking class with us at bakingclub.baileys.com! 🧁🎁🧁
 
Order our #Baileys #RedVelvet cupcakes online for nationwide shipping all month long on georgetowncupcake.com. It’s perfect for treating yourself or gifting your loved ones this Holiday season! 🧁🎁🧁
